sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User / Browser
    participant F as Frontend (React)
    participant A as FastAPI (/api/v1)
    participant P as OAuth Provider
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over U,DB: Login Flow (OAuth 2.0 + PKCE)
    U->>F: Click "Sign in with Google"
    F->>A: POST /auth/login/google
    A-->>F: { authorization_url }
    F->>P: Redirect to authorization_url
    P->>U: Consent screen
    U->>P: Grant consent
    P->>A: GET /auth/callback/google?code=...&state=...
    A->>P: Exchange code for user info
    P-->>A: { email, name, provider_user_id }
    A->>A: Create JWT access + refresh tokens
    A-->>F: { access_token, refresh_token, expires_in }
    F->>F: Store tokens in memory

    Note over U,DB: Authenticated Request
    F->>A: GET /narrators (Authorization: Bearer <access_token>)
    A->>A: Verify JWT signature + expiry
    A->>DB: Query data
    DB-->>A: Results
    A-->>F: 200 JSON response

    Note over U,DB: Token Refresh (before expiry)
    F->>A: POST /auth/refresh { refresh_token }
    A->>A: Verify refresh token, revoke old
    A-->>F: { new_access_token, new_refresh_token }

    Note over U,DB: Logout
    F->>A: POST /auth/logout (Authorization: Bearer <token>)
    A->>A: Revoke tokens
    A-->>F: 204 No Content
